sources.description:
"Let's love tonight," they said, "There may be no tomorrow!"
An American ambulance driver and an English nurse fall in love in Italy during World War I.

Director: Frank Borzage
Writers: Benjamin Glazer, Oliver H.P. Garret, Ernest Hemingway (novel:1929)
Stars: Gary Cooper, Helen Hayes, Adolphe Menjou
Genres: Drama, Literature, Romance, War
